<funcs>
  <func>
    <title>GetDesc</title>
    <category>Objects</category>
    <subcat>Status</subcat>
    <version>4.6.5.0 CP<extversion>4.9.1.0 GWE</extversion></version>
    <syntax><rtype>string</rtype></syntax>
    <desc>Returns the description of an object or of an object definition. Descriptions are stored in the Desc**.txt files of an object definition group.</desc>
    <examples>
      <example>
        <code><funclink>Log</funclink>(&quot;%s|&lt;c ff0000&gt;%s&lt;/c&gt;&quot;, <funclink>GetCursor</funclink>()-&gt;<funclink>GetName</funclink>(), <funclink>GetCursor</funclink>()-&gt;GetDesc());</code>
        <text>Displays a message containing the name of the selected clonk and the description text of the clonk type.</text>
      </example>
    </examples>
  </func>
  <author>Sven2</author><date>2003-06</date>
</funcs>
